derstood topics.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line=
-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">I&#8217;m lucky that there are 100,000+ =
of you smart, curious people who want to explore with me. Please don&#8217;=
t take what I write as the final word. If you&#8217;re interested in a topi=
c I write about, use my piece as a starting point. The best way to approach=
 Not Boring is to <strong>learn </strong><em><strong>with</strong></em><str=
ong> me, not </strong><em><strong>from</strong></em><strong> me</strong>, a=
nd then go off on your own learning adventure.&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: =
#1a1a1a; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">This is go=
ing to be a particularly interesting time &#8211; the <strong>first bear ma=
rket in Not Boring&#8217;s young life</strong>. I&#8217;m almost certainly =
going to write positive pieces about companies and projects whose prices wi=
ll proceed to tank 10% on the very same day. Trolls are going to skewer me,=
 I&#8217;m going to hurt for a second, stew, formulate a witty response, de=
lete it, move on, and hopefully appreciate the absurdity of the fact that t=
hat&#8217;s all part of my job.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p><p style=3D"color: #1a1a1a; =
font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 1em 0;">My worst call ever =
&#8211; <a href=3D"https://email.mg2.substack.com/c/eJxFkMuOwyAMRb-m7BrxcFq=
